Package kodkod.cli

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    KodkodOutput
    Specifies the interface for outputting solutions to Kodkod problems.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractParserTest
    Tests for a rule in the Kodkod parser.
    AllParserTests  
    AssertRuleTest
    Tests for the KodkodParser.Assert() rules.
    ConfigureRuleTest
    Tests for the KodkodParser.Configure() rules.
    ConstraintRuleTest
    Tests for the KodkodParser.Constraint() rules.
    DefEnv
    A definition environment keeps track of definition registers for Kodkod nodes created and referenced during parsing.
    ExprRuleTest
    Tests for the KodkodParser.Expr() rules.
    IntExprRuleTest
    Tests for the KodkodParser.IntExpr() rules.
    IntsRuleTest
    Tests for the KodkodParser.DeclareInts() rules.
    KodkodFactory
    Provides a set of methods that wrap Kodkod's AST, bounds, and options construction methods.
    KodkodFormatter
    Logging formatter.
    KodkodParser
    A PEG parser for a concrete syntax for Kodkod inspired by Kodkodi and SMT-LIB2.
    KodkodProblem
    Provides a set of actions invoked by the Kodkod parser to specify and solve relational satisfiability problems.
    KodkodReporter
    An implementation of the reporter interface that prints messages to a logger.
    KodkodServer
    Provides a server interface to Kodkod.
    NodeRuleTest
    Tests for the KodkodParser.DefNode() rules.
    RelationRuleTest
    Tests for the KodkodParser.DeclareRelation() rules.
    ServerTest
    Tests the interaction with the KodkodServer class.
    StandardKodkodOutput
    An implementation of the KodkodOutput interface that writes solutions provided to it to standard output, in the form of s-expressions.
    TupleSetRuleTest
    Tests for the KodkodParser.TupleSet() rules.
    UniverseRuleTest
    Tests for the KodkodParser.DeclareUniverse() rules.
